== Building your own portfolio [Part 2]

The main goal of this exercise is to become familiar with CSS.
The core concepts that you must be familiar with are:

- What is CSS?
- How to set the language?
- What is a selector?
- The most used selectors
- Embedd CSS with: Tag, inline and external file
- How to add external css file?
- Atributes to take note: background-color, color, font-family, font-size, font-weight, font-style, line-height, text-align, text-decoration

=== Objectives

Building a static website to be your personal portfolio and deploy to GitHub Pages.

=== Pre requisites
:oka: pass:normal[&#10004;]
