Using the HTML tags, your portfolio must meet the following requirementes:

. [{oka}] Set different fonts for your name and a description that you created;
. [{oka}] Define a base color for your Web Portfolio's background;
. [{oka}] Change the style of the tags you know to highlight some information, such as your nationality and the city / state where you live;
. [{oka}] Put different sizes for the elements of the list of skills that you created. Remember to use the classes for each of the elements;